author: Terrence Thomas
title: O’Connor’s eruption too much for Clark
text:
Photo: Tom Reel / San Antonio Express-News Image 1 of / 1 1 Panther receiver Jalen Hughes cuts upfield as O'Connor plays Clark at Farris Stadium on October 15, 2015. Panther receiver Jalen Hughes cuts upfield as O'Connor plays Clark at Farris Stadium on October 15, 2015. Photo: Tom Reel / San Antonio Express-News O’Connor’s eruption too much for Clark 1 / 1 Back to Gallery No. 8 O’Connor scored 35 unanswered points to snap an early tie and rolled past Clark 38-9 in a District 27-6A Zone B game on Thursday before 3,155 at Farris Stadium.
In collecting their sixth straight win in the series, the Panthers (5-2, 2-0) scored two touchdowns in the final five minutes of the first half to break the game open.
For more, visit ExpressNews.com
